<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="281" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="281">
<emphasis box="[199,292,1078,1103]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="281">Remarks</emphasis>
:This species is usually found on sunny, oligotrophic and xerothermic sites, often in quite disturbed pastures (Nickel 
<number box="[681,739,1108,1132]" pageId="8" pageNumber="281" value="2003.0">2003</number>
). In this study some specimens were collected on vineyards floor vegetation and one specimen was unexpectedly collected from vine canopy.
</paragraph>
